Package cz.cuni.mff.d3s.spl.data

Classes for storing and reading data samples and computations of statistics from them.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    BenchmarkRun
    Represents data from a single benchmark run.
    BenchmarkRunUtils.Reducer
    Aggregates all samples from a benchmark run.
    BenchmarkRunUtils.Transformer  
    DataSnapshot
    A snapshot of the performance data.
    DataSource
    Provides access to series of a performance data.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BenchmarkRunBuilder
    Helper class for creating immutable benchmark run.
    BenchmarkRunSummary
    Statistical summary of a benchmark run.
    BenchmarkRunUtils
    Helper methods for working with the BenchmarkRun interface.
    BenchmarkRunUtils.MeanReducer
    Compute mean of a run.
    BenchmarkRunUtils.VarianceNReducer
    Compute variance of a run without bias correction.
    BenchmarkRunUtils.VarianceReducer
    Compute variance of a run.
    BuilderDataSource
    Utility class to read data from streams.
    DataInfo  
    DataSnapshotBuilder
    Helper class for creating data snapshots.
    ImmutableBenchmarkRun
    Immutable implementation of BenchmarkRun that makes and returns always copy of the initial data.
    Revision
    One data revision.
    RingDataSource
    Ring-buffer based data source.
